 First get your VPC ID:
 aws cloudformation describe-stacks --stack-name secureclaims-ai --region ap-south-1 --query "Stacks[0].Outputs[?OutputKey=='VpcId'].OutputValue"  --output text

Check the Network ACLs for that VPC:
aws ec2 describe-network-acls --filters "Name=vpc-id,Values=vpc-0bc5c06837b9d9d80" --region ap-south-1 --query "NetworkAcls[0].[Entries]" --output table

Check security group rules:
aws ec2 describe-security-groups --filters "Name=tag:Name,Values=secureclaims-ec2-sg" --region ap-south-1 --query  "SecurityGroups[0].IpPermissions[].[FromPort,ToPort,IpRanges[0].CidrIp]" --output table

